sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Konflux as Konflux Build System
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>quay.io/rhoai
    participant DSPO as Data Science Pipelines<br/>Operator
    participant InitContainer as Init Container<br/>odh-pipelines-components
    participant SharedVol as Shared Volume<br/>/config/managed-pipelines/
    participant KFP as KFP API Server
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Konflux,SharedVol: Flow 1: Managed Pipeline Initialization
        Konflux->>Registry: Push compiled image<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Robot account auth
        DSPO->>Registry: Pull init container image<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Pull secret
        DSPO->>InitContainer: Deploy as init container
        InitContainer->>SharedVol: Copy pipeline YAMLs<br/>Filesystem (/app/managed-pipelines.json)
        KFP->>SharedVol: Discover managed pipelines<br/>Filesystem read
    end

    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Download as dataset_download<br/>@dsl.component
    participant Train as train_model<br/>(SFT/LoRA/OSFT)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP
    participant Eval as universal_llm_evaluator<br/>@dsl.component
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>443/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference<br/>8000/TCP

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 2: Fine-Tuning Pipeline (SFT/LoRA/OSFT)
        User->>KFP: Submit pipeline run<br/>via RHOAI Dashboard
        KFP->>Argo: Create Argo Workflow
        Argo->>Download: Execute step pod
        Download->>S3: Download training dataset<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS credentials
        Download->>HF: Download model/dataset<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        Download-->>Download: Write to PVC workspace
        Argo->>Train: Execute step pod
        Train->>K8sAPI: Create TrainJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Train-->>Train: Write model to PVC
        Argo->>Eval: Execute step pod
        Eval->>vLLM: Run evaluation<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>No auth (internal)
        Argo->>ModelReg: Execute step pod
        ModelReg->>ModelReg: Register model<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>No auth (internal)
    end

    participant DocsDisc as documents_discovery<br/>@dsl.component
    participant TextExt as text_extraction<br/>@dsl.component
    participant SearchPrep as search_space_preparation<br/>@dsl.component
    participant RAGOpt as rag_templates_optimization<br/>@dsl.component
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack API<br/>443/TCP
    participant Milvus as Milvus<br/>19530/TCP

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,Milvus: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization Pipeline
        User->>KFP: Submit AutoRAG pipeline
        KFP->>Argo: Create Argo Workflow
        Argo->>DocsDisc: Execute step pod
        DocsDisc->>S3: Discover documents<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS credentials
        Argo->>TextExt: Execute step pod
        TextExt->>S3: Fetch raw documents<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS credentials
        Argo->>SearchPrep: Execute step pod
        SearchPrep->>LlamaStack: Generate embeddings<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key
        Argo->>RAGOpt: Execute step pod
        RAGOpt->>LlamaStack: Vector I/O + generation<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key
        RAGOpt->>Milvus: Index documents<br/>gRPC/19530<br/>TLS optional
    end

    participant DataLoader as data_loader<br/>@dsl.component
    participant AutoGluon as autogluon_models_training<br/>@dsl.component
    participant Leaderboard as leaderboard_evaluation<br/>@dsl.component

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
        Note over User,Leaderboard: Flow 4: AutoML Training Pipeline
        User->>KFP: Submit AutoML pipeline
        KFP->>Argo: Create Argo Workflow
        Argo->>DataLoader: Execute step pod
        DataLoader->>S3: Load training CSV/Parquet<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS credentials
        DataLoader-->>DataLoader: Write split data to PVC
        Argo->>AutoGluon: Execute step pod
        AutoGluon-->>AutoGluon: Train models on PVC data
        Argo->>Leaderboard: Execute step pod
        Leaderboard-->>Leaderboard: Evaluate model artifacts
    end
